"Your system's secure memory limit is not enough to securely import the "
"data.\n"
"You need to increase your system's memlock limit by following the "
"instructions on our <a href=\"https://github.com/paolostivanin/OTPClient/"
"wiki/Secure-Memory-Limitations\">secure memory wiki page</a>.\n"
"This requires administrator privileges and is a system-wide setting that "
"OTPClient cannot change automatically."
